    <title>Coptic Dictionary - &#xCD;osl&#xF3;d&#xE1;il agus suite&#xE1;il ar Windows | Microsoft Store</title>
    <base href="/" />

    <meta name="description" content="Coptic Dictionary is an offline Coptic dictionary and study app for Windows.&#xA;&#xA;Search Coptic words, English meanings, romanized type-as spellings, dialect forms, Greek-origin references, and source citations in a fast local desktop app. Save vocabulary as you browse, quiz yourself on saved words, and export study lists for learning, teaching, or research.&#xA;&#xA;The app is built from the Comprehensive Coptic Lexicon v1.2, including Coptic entries and Greek loanword material. It turns scholarly lexicon data into a clean, practical dictionary for Coptic language learners, Egyptology students, researchers, teachers, and anyone studying Coptic vocabulary.&#xA;&#xA;Key tools include offline dictionary search, saved words, quiz mode, forms and dialect labels, source references, Greek-origin indicators, keyboard navigation, study backup import/export, and multiple export formats.&#xA;&#xA;Coptic Dictionary works offline after installation. No account is required. Dictionary searches and saved words stay on your device.&#xA;&#xA;Data source attribution: Comprehensive Coptic Lexicon: Including Loanwords from Ancient Greek, edition v1.2, DOI 10.17169/refubium-27566, licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International.">

