do Thaith\u00ED Windows","Themes.Page.Description":"Faigh agus \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il t\u00E9ama\u00ED, c\u00FAlbhrait, agus roghanna pearsantaithe chun d\u2019eisp\u00E9ireas deisce Windows a shaincheapadh ar Microsoft Store.","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Title":"Pearsantaigh do r\u00EDomhaire","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Subtitle":"Cuir an gl\u00E9as in oiri\u00FAint duit f\u00E9in","Themes.Page.PersonalizeHeader.Description":"Saincheap Windows le paca\u00ED t\u00E9ama coime\u00E1dta - c\u00FAlbhrait nua agus dathanna aicinn","RankDisclosureIcon.Message":"F\u00E9ach {0} chun tuilleadh faisn\u00E9ise a fh\u00E1il faoi chrit\u00E9ir rangaithe","RankDisclosureIcon.AutomationName":"Nochtadh rangaithe","RankDisclosureIcon.HyperlinkText":"F\u00F3gra\u00ED dl\u00ED agus faisn\u00E9is tomhalt\u00F3ra","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.Title":"T\u00E1 br\u00F3n orainn","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.Description":"T\u00E1 brabhs\u00E1la\u00ED n\u00EDos nua\u00ED de dh\u00EDth ar an su\u00EDomh Gr\u00E9as\u00E1in seo le go n-oibreoidh s\u00E9 i gceart.","UnsupportedBrowser.Info.About":"T\u00E1 rochtain agat ar Microsoft Store Gr\u00E9as\u00E1in, \u00E1it ar f\u00E9idir feidhmchl\u00E1ir agus cluich\u00ED a aimsi\u00FA le haghaidh do r\u00EDomhaire.","UnsupportedBrowser.Warning":"T\u00E1 do bhrabhs\u00E1la\u00ED as d\u00E1ta","UnsupportedBrowser.CallToAction":"Nuashonraigh do bhrabhs\u00E1la\u00ED chun amharc ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir, cluich\u00ED agus tuilleadh.","UnsupportedBrowser.CallToAction.Button":"Nuashonraigh anois","VideoPlayer.Actions":"Seinnteoir f\u00EDse\u00E1n. Br\u00FAigh \u0027Enter\u0027 n\u00F3 an sp\u00E1sbharra chun an f\u00EDse\u00E1n a sheinm n\u00F3 \u00E9 a chur ar sos.","VideoPlayer.PlaybackSlider":"Barra sleamhn\u00E1in cuardaigh","VideoPlayer.PlaybackPosition":"{0} soicind\u00ED {1} soicind\u00ED {2} soicind\u00ED {3} soicind\u00ED","VideoPlayer.PlayButton":"Seinn","VideoPlayer.PauseButton":"Cuir ar sos","VideoPlayer.MuteButton":"Balbhaigh","VideoPlayer.Unmut