ge.InstallMultipleButton":"Suite\u00E1il {0} feidhmchl\u00E1ir","AppPackPage.DownloadingButton":"Ag \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il...","AppPackPage.DownloadingStatus":"Ag \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il...","AppPackPage.DownloadingMessage":"T\u00E1imid ag \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il inrite chun na feidhmchl\u00E1ir at\u00E1 roghnaithe agat a shuite\u00E1il. Lainse\u00E1il \u00E9 chun tos\u00FA.","AppPackPage.PostInstallMessage":"D\u0027\u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1ladh comhad inrite chun d\u0027fheidhmchl\u00E1ir a shuite\u00E1il. Lainse\u00E1il \u00F3 \u00CDosl\u00F3d\u00E1lacha chun tos\u00FA. ","AppPackPage.PostInstallMessage-Secondary":"Suite\u00E1lfar roinnt feidhmchl\u00E1r sa ch\u00FAlra.","AppPackPage.RemoveAppAriaLabel":"Bain {0}","AppPackPage.ToggleShoppingCartAriaLabel":"trala\u00ED","AppPackCollection.Productivity":"T\u00E1irgi\u00FAlacht","AppPackCollection.Creativity":"Cruthaitheacht","AppPackCollection.Social":"S\u00F3isialta","AppPackCollection.AI":"AI","AppPackCollection.Entertainment":"Siamsa\u00EDocht","AppPackCollection.ToolsUtilities":"Uirlis\u00ED \u0026 F\u00F3ntais","AppPackCollection.Personalization":"Pearsant\u00FA","AppPackCollection.SelectAppAriaLabel":"Roghnaigh {0}","AppPackCollection.ViewDetailsAriaLabel":"F\u00E9ach ar na sonra\u00ED le haghaidh {0}","AppPackCollection.SignInRequired":"S\u00EDnigh isteach chun an t\u00E1irge seo a fh\u00E1il.","AppPackCollection.VerifyRequired":"N\u00ED m\u00F3r duit an aois at\u00E1 agat a fh\u00EDor\u00FA chun an t\u00E1irge seo a fh\u00E1il.","AppPackCollection.DismissAlertAriaLabel":"Ruaig","ProductGallery.LoadErrorTitle":"N\u00ED f\u00E9idir an feidhmchl\u00E1r a l\u00F3d\u00E1il","ProductGallery.LoadErrorMessage":"N\u00ED f\u00E9idir linn an feidhmchl\u00E1r sin a l\u00F3d\u00E1il. Bain triail as an bhfeidhmchl\u00E1r a chuardach chun triail eile a bhaint as.","ProductEvent.AvailableNow":"Ar f\u00E1il anois","ProductEvent.AvailableOn":"Ar f\u00E1il ar {0}","ProductEvent.Ended":"Cr\u00EDochnaithe","ProductEvent.InOneTimeUnit":"In 1 {0}","ProductEvent.InTime":"In {0} {1}","ProductEvent.OneTimeUnitLeft":"1 {0} amh\u00E1in f\u00E1gtha","ProductEvent.TimeLeft":"{0} {1} f\u00E1gtha","ProductEvent.CardAction":"Tuilleadh eolais maidir le {0}","Collections.curated.best-photo-and-video-editing-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir eagarth\u00F3ireachta grianghraf \u0026 f\u00EDse\u00E1in is fearr do Windows \u2014 na huirlis\u00ED eagarth\u00F3ireachta is fearr don Microsoft Store chun \u00EDomh\u00E1nna a fheabhs\u00FA, f\u00EDse\u00E1in a chruth\u00FA agus me\u00E1in a fheabhs\u00FA.","Collections.curated.racing-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00E1sa\u00EDochta is fearr do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na hinsamhl\u00F3ir\u00ED gluaiste\u00E1n, rothair \u0026 tiom\u00E1na is fearr \u00F3 bhaili\u00FAch\u00E1n cluich\u00ED r\u00E1sa\u00EDochta Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.new-and-notable-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire nua \u0026 suntasacha \u2014 f\u00E9ach thart ar na cluich\u00ED is d\u00E9ana\u00ED agus is m\u00F3 a bhfuil aird \u00E1 tabhairt orthu \u00F3 Microsoft Store i ngach se\u00E1nra do Windows.","Collections.curated.windows-themes.Page.Description":"T\u00E9ama\u00ED Windows \u0026 st\u00EDleanna deisce \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il baili\u00FAch\u00E1in Microsoft Store de ch\u00FAlbhrait, t\u00E9ama\u00ED amhairc agus saincheapadh deisce.","Collections.curated.best-entertainment-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir siamsa\u00EDochta is fearr do Windows \u2014 sruthlaigh ceol, f\u00EDse\u00E1in, podchraolta\u00ED, uirlis\u00ED me\u00E1n \u00F3 na haipeanna is fearr don Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.best-productivity-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta is fearr do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na huirlis\u00ED is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh bainist\u00EDocht tascanna, n\u00F3ta\u00ED a ghlacadh, oibre oifige agus barrfheabhs\u00FA sreafa oibre.","Collections.curated.music-streaming-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir ceoil do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 sruthaigh, cruthaigh agus bain sult as ceol le feidhmchl\u00E1ir fuaime, seinnteoir\u00ED ceoil agus seirbh\u00EDs\u00ED sruthaithe barr Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.social-and-news-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 b\u00ED i dteagmh\u00E1il le cairde, roinn \u00E1bhar agus fan ar an eolas leis na feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00EDonraithe sh\u00F3isialta is fearr sa Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.kids-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED ar Windows \u2014 faigh cluich\u00ED spra\u00ED\u00FAla, s\u00E1bh\u00E1ilte agus oideachas\u00FAla \u00F3n Microsoft Store at\u00E1 foirfe do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED de gach aois.","Collections.curated.most-popular-utility-apps.Page.Description":"Bogearra\u00ED \u00E1irithe do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il uirlis\u00ED riachtanacha \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh optam\u00FA c\u00F3rais, bainist\u00EDocht comhad agus tascanna r\u00EDomhaireachta laeth\u00FAla.","Collections.curated.weather-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir aimsire do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 rianaigh r\u00E9amhaisn\u00E9is\u00ED, d\u00E1la\u00ED aimsire agus fol\u00E1irimh le feidhmchl\u00E1ir aimsire cruinne \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.reading-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00E9itheoireachta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 bain taitneamh as leabhair leictreonacha, ailt agus inneachar digiteach leis na feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00E9itheoireachta agus na leabharlainne is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.remote-learning-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir foghlama do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 f\u00E9ach thart ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir oideachas\u00FAla \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh cianfhoghlama, forbairt scileanna agus c\u00FArsa\u00ED ar l\u00EDne.","Collections.curated.essential-apps.Page.Description":"Aipeanna riachtanacha do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na pr\u00EDomh-aip \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta, cumars\u00E1ide, sl\u00E1nd\u00E1la agus tascanna laeth\u00FAla ar do r\u00EDomhaire.","Collections.curated.best-creativity-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir chruthaitheachta is fearr do Windows \u2014 dearadh, tarraing, cuir in eagar agus cruthaigh le huirlis\u00ED cruthaitheacha barr \u00F3n Microsoft Store d\u0027eala\u00EDont\u00F3ir\u00ED agus d\u00E9ant\u00F3ir\u00ED.","Collections.curated.getting-started-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir tosaithe do r\u00EDomhair\u00ED Windows nua \u2014 cumraigh do ghl\u00E9as le feidhmchl\u00E1ir riachtanacha \u00F3n Microsoft Store do thosaitheoir\u00ED agus d\u0027\u00FAs\u00E1ideoir\u00ED nua.","Collections.curated.personalization-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir phearsantaithe do Windows \u2014 saincheap do dheasc, c\u00FAlbhrait, deilbh\u00EDn\u00ED agus t\u00E9ama\u00ED le huirlis\u00ED pearsanaithe barr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.security-apps.Page.Description":"Aipeanna sl\u00E1nd\u00E1la do Windows \u2014 cosain do r\u00EDomhaire le na pr\u00EDomh-aip frithv\u00EDreas, VPN, bainisteoir pasfhocal agus uirlis\u00ED pr\u00EDobh\u00E1ideachta \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.gaming-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir cluich\u00EDochta do Windows \u2014 ardaigh d\u0027eisp\u00E9ireas cluich\u00EDochta r\u00EDomhaire le sruth\u00FA, comhr\u00E1 gutha, uirlis\u00ED feidhm\u00EDochta agus feidhmchl\u00E1ir chomp\u00E1naigh \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.music-creation-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir cruthaithe ceoil do Windows \u2014 cum, taifead, measc agus t\u00E1irgeadh ceoil le huirlis\u00ED t\u00E1irgthe fuaime agus DAW is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.top-developer-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir forbr\u00F3ra is fearr do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il feidhmchl\u00E1ir ardchaighde\u00E1in \u00F3 fhorbr\u00F3ir\u00ED m\u00F3ra agus foilsitheoir\u00ED iontaofa ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.digital-pen-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir pinn dhigiteacha do Windows \u2014 tarraing, scr\u00EDobh agus an\u00F3t\u00E1il le feidhmchl\u00E1ir Microsoft Store at\u00E1 optamaithe do st\u00EDleas le haghaidh pinn Surface agus gl\u00E9asanna tadhaill.","Collections.curated.kids-educational-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir oideachais do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED ar Windows \u2014 cluich\u00ED foghlama spra\u00ED\u00FAla, l\u00E9itheoireachta, mata agus eola\u00EDochta do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.home-improvement-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir feabhsaithe baile do Windows \u2014 plean\u00E1il athch\u00F3irithe, dearadh int\u00ED, tionscadail DF\u00C9 agus maisi\u00FAch\u00E1n baile le huirlis\u00ED \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.movie-making-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir d\u00E9anta scann\u00E1in do Windows \u2014 cruthaigh, cuir in eagar agus d\u00E9an f\u00EDse\u00E1in le huirlis\u00ED scann\u00E1naithe, beochana agus eagarth\u00F3ireachta f\u00EDse\u00E1in is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.professional-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir ghairmi\u00FAla do Windows \u2014 uirlis\u00ED tionscail \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh innealt\u00F3ireachta, ailtireachta, anail\u00EDse sonra\u00ED agus sreafa\u00ED oibre gn\u00F3.","Collections.curated.best-video-streaming-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir sruth\u00FA f\u00EDse\u00E1in do Windows \u2014 f\u00E9ach scann\u00E1in, cl\u00E1ir teilif\u00EDse agus \u00E1bhar beo leis na seirbh\u00EDs\u00ED sruthaithe agus seinnteoir\u00ED me\u00E1n is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.top-free-apps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir saor in aisce is fearr do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir saor in aisce is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta, siamsa\u00EDochta agus \u00FAs\u00E1ide laeth\u00FAla.","Collections.curated.xbox-play-anywhere-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED Xbox Play Anywhere \u2014 ceannach uair amh\u00E1in, imirt ar Xbox agus PC Windows araon le taca\u00EDocht tras-sh\u00E1bh\u00E1la \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.battery-efficient-apps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir \u00E9ifeachtacha \u00F3 thaobh cadhnra de do Windows \u2014 feidhmchl\u00E1ir \u00E9adroma \u00F3n Microsoft Store at\u00E1 optamaithe le haghaidh saolr\u00E9 fada cadhnra ar r\u00EDomhair\u00ED gl\u00FAine agus t\u00E1ibl\u00E9id.","Collections.curated.core-pc-games.Page.Description":"Pr\u00EDomhchluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach cluich\u00ED Windows is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte i se\u00E1nra\u00ED aicsin, RPG, strait\u00E9ise agus eachtra\u00EDochta ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.classic-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED clasaiceacha r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 tabhair cuairt ar\u00EDs ar do chluich\u00ED is fearr leat agus ar theidil Windows clasaiceacha at\u00E1 ar f\u00E1il ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.casual-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire f\u00E1nacha \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED Windows spra\u00ED\u00FAla, \u00E9asca le foghlaim agus foirfe do sheisi\u00FAin thapa \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.world-building-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire t\u00F3g\u00E1la domhan \u2014 cruthaigh, taisc\u00E9al agus bainistigh do shaolta f\u00E9in i mbosca gainimh, ionsamhl\u00FA agus cluich\u00ED t\u00F3g\u00E1la ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.puzzle-pc-games.Page.Description":"D\u00FAshl\u00E1na\u00EDonn \u2014 cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire meara\u00ED d\u0027intinn le teilit\u00E9ir\u00ED inchinne, puzail loighce \u0026 cluich\u00ED focal \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.indie-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire indie \u2014 faigh cluich\u00ED neamhsple\u00E1cha uath\u00FAla, cruthaitheacha agus duaiseanna buaite \u00F3 fhorbr\u00F3ir\u00ED cumasacha ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.hidden-object-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire oibiacht fholaithe \u2014 aimsigh leideanna, r\u00E9itigh r\u00FAndiamhair agus taisc\u00E9al radhairc sna heachtra\u00ED oibiacht fholaithe is fearr ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.gameloft-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Gameloft \u2014 imir teidil gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta, r\u00E1sa\u00EDochta agus eachtra\u00EDochta coitianta \u00F3 Gameloft at\u00E1 ar f\u00E1il ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.microsoft-casual-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire f\u00E1nacha Microsoft \u2014 bain taitneamh as Solitaire, Mahjong, Minesweeper agus tuilleadh cluich\u00ED f\u00E1nacha saor in aisce \u00F3 Microsoft ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.casino-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Casino \u2014 imir sliot\u00E1in, poker, blackjack \u0026 roulette saor in aisce ar Windows \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.xbox-game-studios-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Xbox Game Studios \u2014 imir Halo, Forza, Age of Empires agus tuilleadh teidil ch\u00E9ad ph\u00E1irt\u00ED \u00F3 Xbox ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.action-and-arcade-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire aicsin agus stuara \u2014 l\u00E1mhach\u00F3ir\u00ED, imreoir\u00ED ard\u00E1in agus clasaicigh stuara ar luas gasta do Windows ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.cooking-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED c\u00F3caireachta do Windows \u2014 bain spraoi as cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe bialainne, b\u00E1c\u00E1la agus cistine \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.battle-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire pearsanta cath \u2014 glac p\u00E1irt i gcomhrac eipici\u00FAil le l\u00E1mhach\u00F3ir\u00ED ilimreora, battle royale agus cluich\u00ED coga\u00EDochta oirbhearta\u00EDocha ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.halo-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Halo \u2014 imir an sainchead\u00FAnas shooter sci-fi c\u00E1ili\u00FAil ar Windows le feachtais, il-imreora agus tuilleadh \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.space-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire sp\u00E1is \u2014 taisc\u00E9al r\u00E9altra\u00ED, p\u00EDol\u00F3t\u00E1il r\u00E9altra\u00ED agus d\u00E9an ceannas ar an gcosmas i gcluich\u00ED ficsin eola\u00EDochta do Windows ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.disney-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Disney \u2014 imir eachtra\u00ED dra\u00EDocht\u00FAla le do charachtair Disney, Pixar, Marvel \u0026 Star Wars is fearr leat ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.warhammer-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Warhammer \u2014 d\u00E9an cogadh sa chruinne grimdark le teidil strait\u00E9ise, gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta agus RPG Warhammer ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.king-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire King \u2014 imir Candy Crush, Farm Heroes agus cluich\u00ED meaitse\u00E1la-3 agus puzail n\u00EDos and\u00FAileacha \u00F3 King ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.big-fish-games-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED Big Fish do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED oibiacht fholaithe, puzail agus eachtra\u00EDochta neamhfhoirme\u00E1lta \u00F3 Big Fish ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.clever-apps-universe.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED Cruinne Feidhmchl\u00E1ir Chliste \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED puzail, ionsamhlaithe agus eachtra\u00EDochta tarraingteacha \u00F3 Clever Apps ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.g5-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED G5 do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED oibiacht fholaithe, meaitse\u00E1la-3 agus eachtra\u00EDochta \u00F3 G5 Entertainment ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.tilting-point-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Tilting Point \u2014 faigh cluich\u00ED strait\u00E9ise, ionsamhlaithe agus eachtra\u00EDochta saor in aisce \u00F3 Tilting Point ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.game-insight-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Game Insight \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED t\u00F3g\u00E1la cathrach, ionsamhlaithe agus strait\u00E9ise \u00F3 Game Insight ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.playrix-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Playrix \u2014 imir Gardenscapes, Homescapes, Township agus eachtra\u00ED meaitse\u00E1la-3 eile \u00F3 Playrix ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.miracle-games-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED Miracle do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED RPG, strait\u00E9ise agus gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta \u00F3 Miracle Games ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.weekly-pc-games-deals.Page.Description":"Marga\u00ED seachtaini\u00FAla do chluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 s\u00E1bh\u00E1il go m\u00F3r le lascain\u00ED seachtaini\u00FAla rothlacha ar chluich\u00ED Windows coitianta \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.instant-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED meandracha \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED saor in aisce bunaithe ar bhrabhs\u00E1la\u00ED l\u00E1ithreach gan aon \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il ag teast\u00E1il, d\u00EDreach \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.more-instant-games.Page.Description":"Tuilleadh cluich\u00ED meandracha \u2014 faigh cluich\u00ED breise saor in aisce bunaithe ar bhrabhs\u00E1la\u00ED le himirt l\u00E1ithreach gan aon \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.tencent-pc-games.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Tencent \u2014 imir teidil cluich\u00EDochta m\u00F3ib\u00EDleacha go r\u00EDomhaire pearsanta coitianta \u00F3 Tencent at\u00E1 ar f\u00E1il ar an Microsoft Store do Windows.","Collections.curated.in-game-deals.Page.Description":"Marga\u00ED inchluiche \u2014 s\u00E1bh\u00E1il ar DLC, pasanna s\u00E9as\u00FAir, airgeadra f\u00EDor\u00FAil agus \u00E1bhar inchluiche do do chluich\u00ED Windows is fearr leat ar an Microsoft Store.","Collections.curated.live-in-game-events.Page.Description":"Imeachta\u00ED beo sa chluiche \u2014 faigh amach faoi imeachta\u00ED teoranta ama, \u00E1bhar s\u00E9as\u00FArach agus d\u00FAshl\u00E1in speisialta at\u00E1 ar si\u00FAl anois i gcluich\u00ED \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopFree.Page.Description":"Baili\u00FAch\u00E1n feidhmchl\u00E1r Windows saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir is fearr don Microsoft Store, lena n-\u00E1ir\u00EDtear uirlis\u00ED t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta, f\u00F3ntais agus siamsa\u00EDochta.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire agus Windows saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh \u00F3 Microsoft Store, cluich\u00ED aicsin, puzail agus strait\u00E9ise.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopPaid.Page.Description":"Baili\u00FAch\u00E1n feidhmchl\u00E1r Windows \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir is fearr don Microsoft Store, lena n-\u00E1ir\u00EDtear uirlis\u00ED t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta, f\u00F3ntais agus siamsa\u00EDochta.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire agus Windows \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED, cluich\u00ED aicsin, puzail agus strait\u00E9ise ag teacht chun cinn \u00F3 Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.Bestphotoandvideoeditingapps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir eagarth\u00F3ireachta grianghraf \u0026 f\u00EDse\u00E1in is fearr do Windows \u2014 na huirlis\u00ED eagarth\u00F3ireachta is fearr don Microsoft Store chun \u00EDomh\u00E1nna a fheabhs\u00FA, f\u00EDse\u00E1in a chruth\u00FA agus me\u00E1in a fheabhs\u00FA.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir Windows ag teacht chun cinn \u2014 faigh amach cad at\u00E1 ag teacht chun cinn anois in Microsoft Store: feidhmchl\u00E1ir t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta, cruthaitheachta agus siamsa\u00EDochta.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire \u0026 Windows ag teacht chun cinn \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED ag teacht chun cinn in Microsoft Store, teidil trasna se\u00E1nra\u00ED agus ard\u00E1in.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Games.Primary.RacingGames._RacingGames.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00E1sa\u00EDochta is fearr do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na hinsamhl\u00F3ir\u00ED gluaiste\u00E1n, rothair \u0026 tiom\u00E1na is fearr \u00F3 bhaili\u00FAch\u00E1n cluich\u00ED r\u00E1sa\u00EDochta Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Games.Primary.NewAndNotablePCGames._NewAndNotablePCGames.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire nua \u0026 suntasacha \u2014 f\u00E9ach thart ar na cluich\u00ED is d\u00E9ana\u00ED agus is m\u00F3 a bhfuil aird \u00E1 tabhairt orthu \u00F3 Microsoft Store i ngach se\u00E1nra do Windows.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopGrossing.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir Windows is m\u00F3 ioncam a ghini\u00FAint \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir Microsoft Store a ghineann an t-ioncam is airde, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire \u0026 Windows is m\u00F3 ioncam a ghini\u00FAint \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na teidil is m\u00F3 ioncam a th\u00E1irgeadh don Microsoft Store agus na cluich\u00ED is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta.","Collections.Curated.WindowsThemes.Page.Description":"T\u00E9ama\u00ED Windows \u0026 st\u00EDleanna deisce \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il baili\u00FAch\u00E1in Microsoft Store de ch\u00FAlbhrait, t\u00E9ama\u00ED amhairc agus saincheapadh deisce.","Collections.Computed.Apps.Deal.Page.Description":"Tairiscint\u00ED \u0026 lascain\u00ED aipeanna do Windows \u2014 faigh tairiscint\u00ED teoranta agus aipeanna \u0026 pac\u00E1ist\u00ED Microsoft Store ar lascaine.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Page.Description":"Tairiscint\u00ED \u0026 lascain\u00ED cluich\u00ED do Windows \u2014 faigh tairiscint\u00ED teoranta agus cluich\u00ED \u0026 pac\u00E1ist\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire Microsoft Store ar lascaine.","Collections.Computed.Apps.MostPopular.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir Windows is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir \u2014 faigh amach feidhmchl\u00E1ir Microsoft Store at\u00E1 ag treocht agus a \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1ladh ag milli\u00FAin \u00FAs\u00E1ideoir\u00ED.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.Page.Description":"Aims\u00EDonn cluich\u00ED r\u00EDomhaire is m\u00F3 \u2014 a bhfuil t\u00F3ir orthu Microsoft Store cluich\u00ED a imr\u00EDonn na milli\u00FAin cluich\u00ED ar fud an domhain.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9alta is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar chluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9ala ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta a bhfuil gr\u00E1 ag na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED d\u00F3ibh ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach faoi na cluich\u00ED comharchumainn, na cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus na heachtra\u00ED sc\u00E9alta is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9alta is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9alta is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9alta is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.ActionAdventure.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eachtra\u00EDochta gn\u00EDomha\u00EDochta ag teacht chun cinn do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED comhoibr\u00EDocha, cluich\u00ED domhanda oscailte agus eachtra\u00ED faoi thiom\u00E1int sc\u00E9alta ag teacht chun cinn ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.CardBoard.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED c\u00E1rta agus 