Computed.Games.MostPopular.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is bre\u00E1 leis na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is d\u00E9ana\u00ED do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED, do mhic l\u00E9inn \u0026 do fhoghlaim leana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is fearr do leana\u00ED agus do scol\u00E1ir\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta do leana\u00ED, do mhic l\u00E9inn agus do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte do leana\u00ED agus do scol\u00E1ir\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Educational.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED oideachas\u00FAla is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta do leana\u00ED, do mhic l\u00E9inn agus do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.FamilyKids.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED teaghlaigh agus leana\u00ED rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED teaghlaigh do leana\u00ED, cluich\u00ED boird teaghlaigh agus cean\u00E1in athaontaithe is fearr r\u00E1t\u0