TopTrending.FamilyKids.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED teaghlaigh agus leana\u00ED ag teacht chun cinn do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED teaghlaigh do leana\u00ED, cluich\u00ED boird teaghlaigh agus cean\u00E1in teacht le ch\u00E9ile ag teacht chun cinn ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, na cluich\u00ED troda anime is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Fighting.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED troda do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar chluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, ar chluich\u00ED troda anime agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh ar do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na milli\u00FAin cluich\u00ED troda is bre\u00E1 leis na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach faoi na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, na cluich\u00ED troda anime agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, n cluich\u00ED troda anime is fearr agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, cluich\u00ED troda anime agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, na cluich\u00ED troda anime is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Fighting.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED troda ag teacht chun cinn do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED troda sr\u00E1ide, na cluich\u00ED troda anime ag teacht chun cinn agus n\u00EDos m\u00F3 ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is airde r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"D\u00E9ile\u00E1lacha ar chluich\u00ED MOBA do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ama ar chluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Imr\u00EDonn na cluich\u00ED MOBA is \u2014 m\u00F3 a bhfuil t\u00F3ir orthu ar r\u00EDomhaire na milli\u00FAin cluich\u00ED MOBA ar a Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is d\u00E9ana\u00ED agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA saor in aisce is fearr do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is fearr agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA is m\u00F3 tuilleamh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA \u00EDoctha is fearr do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is airde r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.MultiPlayerOnlineBattleArena.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED MOBA at\u00E1 ag treocht\u00E1il do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED MOBA ioma\u00EDocha is m\u00F3 ag \u00E9ir\u00ED t\u00F3ir agus cathanna mob ar l\u00EDne anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir teidil faoi cheol f\u00EDschluich\u00ED, imirt rithime agus cluich\u00EDocht le t\u00E9ama ceoil is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Music.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED ceoil do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar cheol faoi chluich\u00ED, ar cheol f\u00EDse\u00E1nchluich\u00ED agus ar theidil rithime ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.Music.Page.Description":"Na cluich\u00ED ceoil eile is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ceoil a bhfuil gr\u00E1 ag na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED d\u00F3ibh ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach faoi na cluich\u00ED ceoil is d\u00E9ana\u00ED faoi chluich\u00ED, na ceol f\u00EDse\u00E1nchluich\u00ED agus na teidil rithime at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir teidil faoi cheol f\u00EDschluich\u00ED, imirt rithime agus cluich\u00EDocht le t\u00E9ama ceoil is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il ceol at\u00E1 ag teacht chun cinn faoi chluich\u00ED, ceol f\u00EDschluich\u00ED agus na teidil rithime at\u00E1 ar f\u00E1il anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir teidil faoi cheol f\u00EDschluich\u00ED, imirt rithime agus cluich\u00EDocht le t\u00E9ama ceoil is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Music.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ceoil at\u00E1 ag treocht\u00E1il do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il ceol at\u00E1 ag teacht chun cinn faoi chluich\u00ED, ceol f\u00EDschluich\u00ED agus teidil rithime at\u00E1 ar f\u00E1il anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile \u00EDoctha rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED eile, cluich\u00ED \u201Cb\u00ED eolach ar a ch\u00E9ile\u201D \u0026 seoda eile is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Other.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED eile do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar chluich\u00ED eile, agus cuir aithne ar chluich\u00ED \u00E9ags\u00FAla agus seoda ceilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED eile a bhfuil gr\u00E1 ag na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED d\u00F3ibh ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach na cluich\u00ED eile is fearr, na cluich\u00ED chun aithne a chur a ch\u00E9ile \u0026 seoda eile is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED eile is fearr, cluich\u00ED chun aithne a chur a ch\u00E9ile \u0026 seoda eile ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il cluich\u00ED eile, cluich\u00ED chun aithne a chur ar a ch\u00E9ile ag teacht chun cinn agus seoda eile is fearr anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED eile, cluich\u00ED \u201Cb\u00ED eolach ar a ch\u00E9ile\u201D \u0026 seoda eile ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Other.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED eile ag teacht chun cinn do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il cluich\u00ED eile, cluich\u00ED chun aithne a chur ar a ch\u00E9ile ag teacht chun cinn agus seoda eile anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, na heachtra\u00ED puzail agus na hard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Platformer.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar chluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, ar eachtra\u00EDochta puzail agus ar ard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.Platformer.Page.Description":"Na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in a bhfuil gr\u00E1 ag na milli\u00FAin imreoir\u00ED d\u00F3ibh ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.New.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh amach faoi na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, na heachtra\u00EDochta puzail agus na hard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach eisithe ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, eachtra\u00ED puzail agus ard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta, na heachtra\u00ED puzail agus na hard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in \u00EDoctha is fearr do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, eachtra\u00ED puzail agus ard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Platformer.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in ag teacht chun cinn do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED ard\u00E1in, eachtra\u00ED puzail agus ard\u00E1in uaf\u00E1is ag teacht chun cinn anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.PuzzleTrivia.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED puzail rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED puzail, puzail meara\u00ED agus cluich\u00ED f\u00EDric\u00ED is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.PuzzleTrivia.Page.Description":"Lascaine ar chluich\u00ED puzail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar chluich\u00ED puzail, ar phuzail m\u00EDreanna meara\u00ED agus ar chluich\u00ED f\u00EDric\u00ED ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.MostPopular.PuzzleTrivia.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED puzail is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do r\u00EDomhaire \u