":"Cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe nua do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir na cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saoil, na cluich\u00ED insamhl\u00F3ra t\u00E1ibl\u00E9id agus na hinsamhl\u00F3ir\u00ED cluich\u00ED ocrais is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopFree.Simulation.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saor is aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saoil, cluich\u00ED insamhl\u00F3ra t\u00E1ibl\u00E9id agus ionsamhl\u00F3ir cluich\u00ED ocrais is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopGrossing.Simulation.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe is m\u00F3 tuillte do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saoil, cluich\u00ED ionsamhl\u00F3ra boird agus ionsamhl\u00F3ir cluich\u00ED ocrais is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopPaid.Simulation.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saoil, cluich\u00ED insamhl\u00F3ra t\u00E1ibl\u00E9id agus ionsamhl\u00F3ir cluich\u00ED ocrais is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.TopTrending.Simulation.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe treochta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il cluich\u00ED ionsamhlaithe saoil a bhfuil t\u00F3ir orthu agus ag teacht chun cinn, cluich\u00ED insamhl\u00F3ra boird agus ionsamhl\u00F3ir\u00ED cluich\u00ED ocrais anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.BestRated.Social.Page.Description":"Na cluich\u00ED s\u00F3isialta rogha an phobail do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 imir cluich\u00ED asbhainte s\u00F3isialta, cluich\u00ED il-imreora ar l\u00EDne agus cluich\u00ED r\u00E9alta rac-cheoil is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Games.Deal.Social.Page.Description":"Marga\u00ED cluich\u00ED s\u00F3isialta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00