"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir st\u00EDl mhaireacht\u00E1la ag teacht chun cinn do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir st\u00EDl mhaireacht\u00E1la, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir faisin agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir bhaile is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.BestRated.Medical.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis rogha an phobail do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ch\u00FAir\u00E9ireachta leighis is fearr agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir giorr\u00FAch\u00E1n leighis is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.Deal.Medical.Page.Description":"Tairiscint\u00ED feidhmchl\u00E1r leighis do Windows \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir ch\u00FAir\u00E9ireachta leighis agus ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir giorr\u00FAch\u00E1n leighis is fearr ag Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.MostPopular.Medical.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do Windows \u2014 faigh amach faoi na feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1ilte ag na milli\u00FAin daoine ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.New.Medical.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis nua do Windows \u2014 faigh amach na feidhmchl\u00E1ir c\u00FAir\u00E9ireachta leighis is d\u00E9ana\u00ED \u0026 na feidhmchl\u00E1ir giorr\u00FAch\u00E1n leighis is fearr at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach curtha le Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopFree.Medical.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis saor is aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ch\u00FAir\u00E9ireachta leighis is fearr agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir giorr\u00FAch\u00E1n leighis is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopGrossing.Medical.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir leighis is m\u00F3 tuillte do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ch\u00FAir\u00E9ireachta leighis agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir gior