e is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta, feidhmchl\u00E1ir imreora me\u00E1n agus sruth\u00FA me\u00E1n is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopGrossing.Media.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n is m\u00F3 tuillte do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta, feidhmchl\u00E1ir seinnteoir me\u00E1n a bhfuil t\u00F3ir orthu agus ag teacht chun cinn agus sruth\u00FA me\u00E1n ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopPaid.Media.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta, feidhmchl\u00E1ir imreora me\u00E1n agus sruth\u00FA me\u00E1n is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.Media.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n at\u00E1 ag treocht\u00E1il do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta, feidhmchl\u00E1ir seinnteoir me\u00E1n a bhfuil t\u00F3ir orthu agus ag teacht chun cinn agus sruth\u00FA me\u00E1n anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.BestRated.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha \u00EDoctha rogha an phobail do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha aipeanna soghluaiste, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00EDrdhreacha agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha int\u00ED is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.Deal.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Tairiscint\u00ED feidhmchl\u00E1r ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha do Windows \u2014 faigh lascain\u00ED agus tairiscint\u00ED teoranta ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha ar fheidhmchl\u00E1r m\u00F3ib\u00EDleach, ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00EDrdhreacha agus ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha int\u00ED ag Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.MostPopular.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n \u0026 deartha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 faigh amach faoi na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n \u0026 deartha a \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1ladh ag na milli\u00FAin ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.New.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n \u0026 deartha nua do Windows \u2014 faigh amach na feidhmchl\u00E1ir dearaidh aip mh\u00F3ib\u00EDleach, feidhmchl\u00E1ir dearaidh t\u00EDrdhreacha \u0026 feidhmchl\u00E1ir dearaidh int\u00ED is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 d\u00EDreach curtha le Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopFree.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha aipeanna soghluaiste, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00EDrdhreacha agus feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha int\u00ED is fearr ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopGrossing.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha is m\u00F3 tuillte do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha aipeanna soghluaiste, feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00EDrdhreacha agus feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha int\u00ED is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopPaid.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha \u00EDoctha is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha aipeanna soghluaiste, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00EDrdhreacha agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha int\u00ED is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.MultimediaDesign.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir ilmhe\u00E1n agus deartha at\u00E1 ag teacht chun cinn do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha aipeanna soghluaiste, na feidhmchl\u00E1ir deartha t\u00E