 teoranta ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais aerfoirt, ar uirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1ir agus ar feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucail\u00ED ag Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.MostPopular.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED is m\u00F3 \u00E9ilimh do Windows \u2014 faigh amach faoi na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED at\u00E1 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1ilte ag na milli\u00FAin daoine ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.New.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED nua do Windows \u2014 faigh amach faoi na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais aerfoirt, na huirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1ir agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucail\u00ED is d\u00E9ana\u00ED at\u00E1 curtha le Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopFree.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED saor in aisce is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais aerfoirt, na huirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1r agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucail\u00ED is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopGrossing.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED is m\u00F3 tuillte do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir \u00E1irg\u00ED aerfoirt, uirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1r agus feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucaile is m\u00F3 d\u00EDolta ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopPaid.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED is m\u00F3 t\u00F3ir do Windows \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais aerfoirt, na huirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1r agus na feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucail\u00ED is fearr r\u00E1t\u00E1ilte ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Computed.Apps.TopTrending.UtilitiesTools.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais agus uirlis\u00ED at\u00E1 teacht chun cinn do Windows \u2014 brabhs\u00E1il na feidhmchl\u00E1ir f\u00F3ntais aerfoirt, uirlis\u00ED forbartha feidhmchl\u00E1r agus feidhmchl\u00E1ir uirlis\u00ED trucail\u00ED ag teacht chun cinn anois ar Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.BestEntertainmentApps._BestEntertainmentApps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir siamsa\u00EDochta is fearr do Windows \u2014 sruthlaigh ceol, f\u00EDse\u00E1in, podchraolta\u00ED, uirlis\u00ED me\u00E1n \u00F3 na haipeanna is fearr don Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.Bestproductivityapps._Bestproductivityapps.Page.Description":"Na feidhmchl\u00E1ir t\u00E1irgi\u00FAlachta is fearr do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il na huirlis\u00ED is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh bainist\u00EDocht tascanna, n\u00F3ta\u00ED a ghlacadh, oibre oifige agus barrfheabhs\u00FA sreafa oibre.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ExploreAWorldOfMusic._ExploreAWorldOfMusic.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir ceoil do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 sruthaigh, cruthaigh agus bain sult as ceol le feidhmchl\u00E1ir fuaime, seinnteoir\u00ED ceoil agus seirbh\u00EDs\u00ED sruthaithe barr Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ConnectAndStayInformed._ConnectAndStayInformed.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir me\u00E1n s\u00F3isialta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 b\u00ED i dteagmh\u00E1il le cairde, roinn \u00E1bhar agus fan ar an eolas leis na feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00EDonraithe sh\u00F3isialta is fearr sa Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Games.Primary.PCGamesForKids._PCGamesForKids.Page.Description":"Cluich\u00ED do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED ar Windows \u2014 faigh cluich\u00ED spra\u00ED\u00FAla, s\u00E1bh\u00E1ilte agus oideachas\u00FAla \u00F3n Microsoft Store at\u00E1 foirfe do ph\u00E1ist\u00ED de gach aois.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.MostPopularUtilityApps._MostPopularUtilityApps.Page.Description":"Bogearra\u00ED \u00E1irithe do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 \u00EDosl\u00F3d\u00E1il uirlis\u00ED riachtanacha \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh optam\u00FA c\u00F3rais, bainist\u00EDocht comhad agus tascanna r\u00EDomhaireachta laeth\u00FAla.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.WeatherApps._WeatherApps.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir aimsire do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 rianaigh r\u00E9amhaisn\u00E9is\u00ED, d\u00E1la\u00ED aimsire agus fol\u00E1irimh le feidhmchl\u00E1ir aimsire cruinne \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.ReadingRoom._ReadingRoom.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00E9itheoireachta do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 bain taitneamh as leabhair leictreonacha, ailt agus inneachar digiteach leis na feidhmchl\u00E1ir l\u00E9itheoireachta agus na leabharlainne is fearr \u00F3n Microsoft Store.","Collections.Curated.MerchandiserContent.Apps.Primary.AppsForLearningRemotely._AppsForLearningRemotely.Page.Description":"Feidhmchl\u00E1ir foghlama do r\u00EDomhaire \u2014 f\u00E9ach thart ar fheidhmchl\u00E1ir oideachas\u00FAla \u00F3n Microsoft Store le haghaidh cianfhoghlama, forbairt scileanna agus c\u00FArsa\u00ED ar l\u00EDne.","Collection.Filter.AllProducts":"T\u00E1irg\u00ED uile","Collection.Filter.AllCategories":"Gach catag\u00F3ir","Collection.Filter.AllGenres":"Gach se\u00E1nra","Collection.Filter.AllSubscriptions":"Gach s\u00EDnti\u00FAs","Collection.Filter.AnyPlayers":"Aon l\u00EDon imreoir\u00ED","Collection.Filter.AllStudios":"Gach sti\u00FAideo","Collection.Filter.AllNetworks":"Gach l\u00EDonra","Collection.Filter.Specials":"Tairiscint\u00ED speisialta","Collection.Filter.SortByTitle":"S\u00F3rt\u00E1il de r\u00E9ir:","Collection.Filter.SortByAriaLabel":"S\u00F3rt\u00E1il de r\u00E9ir {0}","Collection.Filter.CollectionAriaLabel":"Baili\u00FAch\u00E1n","Collection.Fi